schools.name: Cobalt Institute Of Math And Science Academy

data.description: HOME SWEET HOME! Lovely one story home located in the growing city of Adelanto. Inside the home is a spacious split floor plan with 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. This house features two formal living rooms with a dual area fireplace. Expect to be welcomed to an open-concept interior that displays combination of vibrant and neutral tones, easy-care tiles, and you will enjoy a brightly lit dining and family room with natural light. The master bedroom enjoys a Jake and Jill sink for his and her, spacious walk in closet, individual shower and bathtub. For entertaining guest and large events there is spacious backyard. There is a spacious two car garage with automatic door opener. The backyard is an open canvas with plenty of potential including a pool and spa. Priced to sell by a motivated seller.
